ments in India. The company supplies bulk and packed bitumen, and other bituminous products, as well as offers bitumen 60/70 and 80/100; bitumen VG10, VG30, and VG 40; bitumen emulsion, blown bitumen, and micro surfacing bitumen; and modified bitumen CRMB, PMB, and NRMB. The company imports, exports, and trades in bitumen. In addition, it provides consultancy services for setting up of plants for bitumen and bituminous products. The company's products are used in construction of roads and highways; surfacing of road and pavements; and as an adhesive substance in the production of binders. It serves various distributors and corporates. The company was incorporated in 2016 and is headquartered in Mumbai, India."}}